{{Amgrad icqqan}}

Amḍan <math>e</math>, ittawsan s ddu ism n [[amḍan]] n [[Euler]], iga yat timgzit n tusnakt iqqrb nit aygadda d 2.71828, nzḍar ad tt nara s mnnaw tɣarasin. Iga uzadur n [[Alugaritm agaman|ulugaritm agaman]]<ref>https://mathvault.ca/hub/higher-math/math-symbols/ . ''Math Vault''. 2020-03-01.</ref>, iga daɣ talast n <math>(1 + 1/n)^n</math> iɣ taẓ <math>n</math> i wartmi. Nzḍar ad tt daɣ nara s yat tɣarasin ilan timrnit, zund ɣikad :

<math>e =  \sum\limits_{n = 0}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n!} = \frac{1}{1} + \frac{1}{1} + \frac{1}{1\cdot 2} + \frac{1}{1\cdot 2\cdot 3} + \cdots</math>

== Amawal ==

* Timgzit : constante
* Talast : limite
* Wartmi : Infinie

